I think that you disregard the importance of a bolt range spell that "just disrupts".  I think that amnesia has much more general utility in RvR than does mez (at least right now).  I can stand and chain cast amnesia at range while the tanks close the distance, while I'm doing that, their archers can't fire and their casters can't cast.  I can mez once the battle ensues.  I think it's a highly under used spell.<P>What I would love to see in RvR is Sorcs getting RPs for our non-DD spells. If the target dies under the effects of one of our debuffs or mezzes then we should get RP.<P>--------------------<P>Badea<BR>Sorceress Bedevere
