Aye, they said some time ago they were working to revamp the whole pet system....but we haven't heard anything on that lately.<P>Indeed, our pets need to work at bolt range, at least.  That's a valiant struggle i3ullseye, I commend ye on it.<P>But, while they're revamping the pet system, what I would like to see are more command options.  I don't mind if the pet window is a little bigger...but I think it'd be interesting to have us be able to command our pet to do the special attacks that they're capable of.  You see people here discussing how to make an archer fire arrows, and how to make an Isolationist Cleric cast this spell or that spell...it'd be more complex, but it would be strategically useful to be able to have a "special commands" window for all those neat abilities, and allow us to control when the pet does them.
